16:42.652 --> 16:44.575
Light is a gift.

16:46.457 --> 16:47.838
Yeah.

16:47.858 --> 16:52.364
This idea, this concept of light, well, God is light in him.

16:52.384 --> 16:53.465
There is no darkness at all.

16:53.505 --> 16:57.970
