17:40.151 --> 17:41.814
The chef has thought of everything.

17:42.074 --> 17:46.601
This is how God designed the world with you in mind.

17:47.883 --> 17:50.608
You see Advent makes us think a little deeper.

17:51.349 --> 17:52.290
Think with me for a second.

17:53.272 --> 17:54.674
To an infinite artist,

17:55.586 --> 18:06.318
a creator in love with his craft, there is no unimportant corner, there is no throwaway image, no tattered thread in the novel left on time.

18:07.880 --> 18:16.309
So when God was forming the world, he spoke light into the darkness, and light is not ordinary.

